Summary[edit]

DescriptionFlag of Northern Ireland.svg
English: The flag of Northern Ireland from 1953 with Edwardian crown since coronation of Queen Elizabeth II, based earlier design with Tudor Crown from 1924. Otherwise known as the Ulster Flag, Ulster Banner, Red Hand of Ulster Flag, Red Hand Flag.
العربية: علم إيرلندا الشمالية
Date 1 January 1973
Source My rework of well-known design
Author Mamadou
